name: 3 X 2k off, 1k on + cool down
description: Was intending on a 4:30 pace to emulate 10k goal pace, was feeling really fresh out of the gate with the 4:22 on the 1st. Felt solid, but harder than I’d actually wanna go off the start cus I’d for sure fall off. The 2nd was closest to 4:30 but felt pretty tough then for the last I figured I’d just go all out haha. Honestly stoked with the 4:10 especially with it being the 9th k - was not expecting that. Gonna hopefully get #1 on those segments someday. Overall felt like a good comeback after yesterday had me bummed.
